flowchart LR
  U[unknown]
  P[partial]
  K[known]
  V[verified]
  R[regressed]

  U -->|observe / detect| P
  P -->|fresh full evidence| K
  K -->|passes success criterion| V
  V -->|change breaks it| R
  R -->|re-observe + fix| P
  R -->|hotfix + verify| V
  P -->|user accepts as-is| K

  classDef good fill:#d4f7d4,stroke:#2d7a2d,color:#000;
  classDef bad fill:#f7d4d4,stroke:#7a2d2d,color:#000;
  class V good
  class R bad
